OL,3,COBR Chair Richard Hughes resigns after
OL,4,CBudget leak
OL,6,FThe chair of the Office for Budget
OL,7,FResponsibility (OBR) has resigned in
OL,8,Fthe wake of the watchdog's leaking of
OL,9,Fdetails of the chancellor's Budget.
OL,11,FRichard Hughes said he had done so in
OL,12,Forder for the watchdog to "quickly
OL,13,Fmove on from this regrettable
OL,14,Fincident", in his letter to Rachel
OL,15,FReeves and Dame Meg Hillier, Chair of
OL,16,Fthe Treasury Select Committee.
