OL,3,COBR Chair Richard Hughes resigns after
OL,4,CBudget leak
OL,6,FIt comes after the OBR's investigation
OL,7,Finto the incident was published on
OL,8,FMonday afternoon, concluding the leak
OL,9,Fof its Economic and Fiscal Outlook
OL,10,F(EFO) before last Wednesday's Budget
OL,11,Fwas the "worst failure" in the
OL,12,Fwatchdog's history.
OL,14,FMr Hughes wrote that he took "full
OL,15,Fresponsibility to the shortcomings
OL,16,Fidentified in the report", which
OL,17,Fstrongly criticised the watchdog's
OL,18,Fprocesses for protecting sensitive
OL,19,Finformation.
OL,26,@sD@IOUsD@WO]
