OL,3,COBR Chair Richard Hughes resigns after
OL,4,CBudget leak
OL,6,F"I also need to play my part in
OL,7,Fenabling the organisation that I have
OL,8,Floved leading for the past five years
OL,9,Fto quickly move on from this
OL,10,Fregrettable incident," he wrote.
OL,12,F"I have, therefore, decided it is in
OL,13,Fthe best interest of the OBR for me to
OL,14,Fresign as its Chair and take full
OL,15,Fresponsibility to the shortcomings
OL,16,Fidentified in the report."
