OL,3,COBR Chair Richard Hughes resigns after
OL,4,CBudget leak
OL,6,FHe added: "By implementing the
OL,7,Frecommendations in this report, I am
OL,8,Fcertain the OBR can quickly regain and
OL,9,Frestore the confidence and esteem that
OL,10,Fit has earned through 15 years of
OL,11,Frigorous, independent economic
OL,12,Fanalysis."
OL,14,FMr Hughes has served as chairman of
OL,15,Fthe watchdog, which is responsible for
OL,16,Fanalysing the policies announced by
OL,17,Fthe government to see how they will
OL,18,Fimpact the economy, since 2020.
