OL,3,COBR Chair Richard Hughes resigns after
OL,4,CBudget leak
OL,6,FHe was reappointed to the job for a
OL,7,Fsecond five-year term in July this
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FSpeaking in the Commons as the news of
OL,11,Fthe resignation broke, Chief Secretary
OL,12,Fto the Treasury James Murray offered
OL,13,Fthe government's thanks to Mr Hughes
OL,14,F"for his dedication to public service".
