OL,3,COBR Chair Richard Hughes resigns after
OL,4,CBudget leak
OL,6,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,7,Faccused the chancellor of using Mr
OL,8,FHughes as a "human shield" and
OL,9,Freiterated her calls for Reeves to
OL,10,Fresign over allegations she misled
OL,11,Fvoters over the state of the public
OL,12,Ffinances in order to raise taxes.
OL,14,FFollowing last week's unprecedented
OL,15,Fbreach, the OBR launched an
OL,16,Finvestigation with expert input from
OL,17,FProfessor Ciaran Martin, former head
OL,18,Fof the National Cyber Security Centre
OL,19,F(NCSC).
