OL,3,COBR Chair Richard Hughes resigns after
OL,4,CBudget leak
OL,6,FIt was "not a case of intentional
OL,7,Fleakage" or a matter of pressing
OL,8,Fpublish too early, according to the
OL,9,Freport released on Monday.
OL,11,FThe investigation found several
OL,12,Fdifferent unique IP addresses that
OL,13,Funsuccessfully attempted 44 times to
OL,14,Faccess the website link containing the
OL,15,FEFO before it was publicly available.
OL,16,FLater, a total of 32 unique IP
OL,17,Faddresses made 43 successful attempts.
